un do hob ikh zikh gedarft oyslernen, di fingers flegn mir zikh nit

00:13:09.201 --> 00:13:14.306
fun bay n- fun bay nakht biz in der fri flegn zayn di fingers azoy tsuzamen gedreyt.

00:13:14.306 --> 00:13:15.914
az ikh hob nit gekent

00:13:16.073 --> 00:13:18.986
oystsien di fingers biz ikh hob zikh oysgelernt.

00:13:19.077 --> 00:13:20.668
nu melkn ki.

00:13:20.668 --> 00:13:22.259
un ale shvere arbet.

00:13:22.266 --> 00:13:23.762
ober dortn

00:13:25.658 --> 00:13:28.591
ikh hob gemerkt az es toyg dortn nit tsu zayn.

00:13:28.591 --> 00:13:29.702
bin ikh avek,

00:13:31.564 --> 00:13:34.438
vi vi aykh tsu zogn in

00:13:34.438 --> 00:13:37.701
in in klo- in kloyster tsu geyn, in

00:13:37.875 --> 00:13:41.193
un ikh bin shoyn merer dortn nit gekumen, bin ikh avek in a ander ort,

00:13:41.318 --> 00:13:45.272
ot azoy hob ikh gevandert, vu a tog, un vu a nakht,

00:13:45.272 --> 00:13:47.623
nit hobndik keyn dakh ibern kop,

00:13:47.815 --> 00:13:51.774
ikh fleg zen a likht,

00:13:51.882 --> 00:13:52.958
fun vaytn,

00:13:52.958 --> 00:13:55.554
fleg ikh geyn in dem rikhtung fun di likht,

00:13:55.678 --> 00:14:01.511
ober ikh hob dokh UNK nit farshtanen az dos iz fosfor, az dos iz blind.

00:14:01.517 --> 00:14:05.235
fleg ikh kumen oyf dem ort fun di likht, flegt es vayter zayn vayter.

00:14:05.235 --> 00:14:08.075
ot azoy fleg ikh durkh geyn durkh tog un durkh nakht.

00:14:09.099 --> 00:14:10.961
vu a tog, vu a nakht.

00:14:10.967 --> 00:14:16.108
ober der forgefil fleg ikh visn vu ontsuklapn di tir un vu nit.

00:14:16.468 --> 00:14:22.689
un nakher az ikh fleg zogn az do hob ikh gevolt onklapn nor di harts hot mir nit gelozn, flegn zey zogn, yo, dortn hot gelebt a bandit.

00:14:23.218 --> 00:14:24.058
nu,

00:14:25.918 --> 00:14:29.540
ot azoy bin ikh geven biz ikh bin gekumen i- in Shavl.

00:14:30.863 --> 00:14:31.937
in Shavl?

00:14:31.906 --> 00:14:33.138
yo, in Shavl.

00:14:33.006 --> 00:14:34.822
UNK zent ir gekumen in Shavl?

00:14:34.255 --> 00:14:35.329
in Shavl.

00:14:35.824 --> 00:14:38.281
un do iz geven eyner

00:14:38.710 --> 00:14:40.999
zeyer a, er iz geven a komunist,

00:14:41.055 --> 00:14:43.496
Tshepaytes, Ervardes.

00:14:48.295 --> 00:14:51.697
vu ikh hob a mol gearbet bay bay zey,

00:14:52.429 --> 00:14:55.967
dortn lebt nit

00:14:56.496 --> 00:15:00.112
nit vayt fun ban linye, dortn iz geven

00:15:00.112 --> 00:15:03.408
a a ⟨derkatshke⟩ ikh vey- vi zogt men dos?

00:15:02.250 --> 00:15:04.184
a vaserl, a vaser kval.

00:15:03.972 --> 00:15:05.344
yo, dortn

00:15:05.344 --> 00:15:08.353
fleg flegn mir arbetn als

00:15:10.131 --> 00:15:13.106
oyframen dortn, kern di di

00:15:13.106 --> 00:15:15.052
es zol zayn zoyber.

00:15:15.193 --> 00:15:19.839
un er i- iz eyner fun di maysters,

00:15:19.839 --> 00:15:21.363
velkhe hobn dortn gearbet,

00:15:22.247 --> 00:15:25.424
geven zeyer a guter, er flegt undz araynfirn in shtub,

00:15:25.424 --> 00:15:30.763
un er flegt lozn undz hern di radyo fun oysland, vu es halt mitn front, vi es halt mit yidn,

00:15:30.769 --> 00:15:33.769
un un er flegt gebn esn alemen,

00:15:33.769 --> 00:15:35.437
zeyer oft mol,

00:15:35.528 --> 00:15:38.711
er er bin ikh dortn gekumen bay zey,

00:15:38.802 --> 00:15:40.061
un zey

00:15:40.270 --> 00:15:43.768
hobn mir, di kinder flegn lernen lernen in shule,

00:15:43.768 --> 00:15:46.338
un di lererke hot gedarft hobn a

00:15:46.497 --> 00:15:48.583
a dinst tsu ir kind.

00:15:48.792 --> 00:15:50.693
hobn zey mir rekomendirt.

00:15:50.884 --> 00:15:53.780
a a shayn,

00:15:54.310 --> 00:15:57.341
a geburts-shayn, a litvishn, hob ikh gehat,

00:15:57.685 --> 00:15:59.721
keyn, farshteyt zikh a falshn.

00:16:00.250 --> 00:16:01.613
ober

00:16:01.613 --> 00:16:05.064
dos, hobn zey mir rekomendirt, ikh bin ongekumen,

00:16:05.064 --> 00:16:06.521
oyf

00:16:06.949 --> 00:16:10.115
in Shavl mit Skevitsher's gas,

00:16:10.155 --> 00:16:14.384
un dem gedenk ikh shoyn nit, dortn iz itster a kindergartn oyf dem ort.

00:16:15.572 --> 00:16:17.557
es iz zeyer merkevdik,

00:16:17.867 --> 00:16:19.025
az

00:16:19.133 --> 00:16:23.382
mir hobn, undz hobn shoyn geven

00:16:23.382 --> 00:16:27.311
es, es iz shoyn geven onfliungen fun di rusn,

00:16:27.317 --> 00:16:30.587
un mentshn hobn oyf in hoyf gegrobn

00:16:30.587 --> 00:16:32.305
sh- shuts-grobns.

00:16:32.599 --> 00:16:33.977
iz

00:16:34.827 --> 00:16:38.713
ober di familye, Katenes hot geheysn,

00:16:38.713 --> 00:16:41.502
er iz geven a artist un a khodozhnik,

00:16:41.577 --> 00:16:42.803
a moler, yo?

00:16:41.644 --> 00:16:43.691
a moler, yo,

00:16:43.691 --> 00:16:45.704
un zi iz geven a lererke.

00:16:45.728 --> 00:16:46.937
oyf litvish.

00:16:47.567 --> 00:16:53.011
hobn zey zikh aroysgeklibn bay di eltern in Marienpol, hobn zey nit gedarft hobn keyn dinst.

00:16:53.322 --> 00:16:56.083
bin ikh geblibn shteyn ot azoy vi

00:16:56.882 --> 00:16:58.884
oyfn gas.

00:16:59.565 --> 00:17:02.951
ir hot gezogt az ir hot gehat a falshn geburts-shayn.

00:17:02.468 --> 00:17:03.289
yo.

00:17:03.025 --> 00:17:05.078
ver hot aykh gemakht dem geburts-shayn?

00:17:04.272 --> 00:17:06.055
der galekh fun Shukyan.

00:17:06.906 --> 00:17:07.794
aha.

00:17:06.973 --> 00:17:08.570
Saservitshus.

00:17:07.952 --> 00:17:09.296
baym shmadn.

00:17:08.982 --> 00:17:09.769
yo.

00:17:09.707 --> 00:17:16.822
aha UNK hot aykh aroge- hot aykh aroysgegebn a flashn geburt-shayn az ir zent Marye, un der familye nomen?

00:17:13.555 --> 00:17:20.535
yo, yo yo. Yaunayka, nit Yavnayka, nor Yaunayka. au.

00:17:22.414 --> 00:17:26.739
un tsugepast di eltern's nemen. der foter hot geheysn Khaim Shimen, hot er gemakht

00:17:26.739 --> 00:17:27.977
Simonas.

00:17:28.117 --> 00:17:29.951
OTAK, ot azoy.

00:17:28.725 --> 00:17:30.862
azoy az es zol zayn gut far litviner.

00:17:30.227 --> 00:17:31.723
yo, es zol durkhgeyn.

00:17:32.286 --> 00:17:33.664
un

00:17:35.897 --> 00:17:40.602
un ikh hob azoy gedint biz ikh hob zikh aroysgeklibn bay di eltern.

00:17:40.602 --> 00:17:43.226
vayle zey hobn shoyn dan nit gedarft keyn dinst,

00:17:43.226 --> 00:17:46.033
bin ikh geblibn shte- shtekn oyfn gas.

00:17:46.292 --> 00:17:50.944
bin ikh gegangen bay di Motskiner,

00:17:51.591 --> 00:17:53.239
zi iz geven a yidishe,

00:17:53.262 --> 00:17:56.648
un ir man iz geven a litvin- a litviner.

00:17:57.126 --> 00:17:59.837
Motskus, zeyer a guter mentsh.

00:18:02.222 --> 00:18:05.152
ir hot zey gekent fun frier, di Motskiner mit Motskusen?

00:18:04.922 --> 00:18:06.876
Motskus iz geven a kelber.

00:18:06.876 --> 00:18:09.222
un er iz geven a FOOTBALList a-

00:18:09.222 --> 00:18:11.362
az al- ale hobn im gekent.

00:18:11.655 --> 00:18:15.263
er do muz ikh aykh dertseyln a merkverdikn fal.

00:18:15.263 --> 00:18:18.771
beshas ikh hob gedint bay di lererke, bay di Katines,

00:18:18.895 --> 00:18:21.735
ge- fleg ikh geyn nokh milkh gants fri

00:18:21.735 --> 00:18:25.025
bay af UNK gas dortn bay a froy,

00:18:25.025 --> 00:18:27.849
nemen fun eyn ku milkh far dem kind.

00:18:28.733 --> 00:18:30.178
iz

00:18:30.623 --> 00:18:31.801
gey ikh,

00:18:31.801 --> 00:18:34.043
un ikh her vi eyner zogt tsu mir,

00:18:34.757 --> 00:18:36.877
"gut morgn, Yavnayke!"

00:18:38.402 --> 00:18:41.602
ikh hob im in flug im nit derkent.

00:18:41.760 --> 00:18:47.326
ober ikh hob shoyn a gantse nakht nit geshlofn, un ikh bin shoyn geven nit ruik oyfn hartsn.

00:18:47.326 --> 00:18:48.572
ober nakher

00:18:48.713 --> 00:18:51.289
hob ikh getrofn di froy,

00:18:54.518 --> 00:18:55.592
Motskener?

00:18:54.788 --> 00:18:57.094
neyn. Di froy.

00:18:59.698 --> 00:19:01.295
vu vu

00:19:01.352 --> 00:19:02.308
Leye.

00:19:04.204 --> 00:19:07.066
Leye nu!

00:19:30.377 --> 00:19:34.151
nit vikhtik, efsher vet ir zikh shpeter dermonen. vos hot dir di froy UNK ⟨gezokht⟩?

00:19:34.225 --> 00:19:36.834
zog ikh, vu lebt,

00:19:36.908 --> 00:19:40.834
ver iz dos aza der un der vos hot zikh mit mir bagrist?

00:19:41.025 --> 00:19:42.352
zogt zi,

00:19:42.443 --> 00:19:44.321
dos iz dokh Motskus velkh-

00:19:44.321 --> 00:19:46.655
velkher lebt do oyf UNK gas.

00:19:46.965 --> 00:19:49.676
gey arayn bay di froy, bay zayne.

00:19:49.750 --> 00:19:51.617
bin ikh arayn, hot zi mir gezogt,

00:19:51.825 --> 00:19:53.695
mir hobn, zogt zi, a

00:19:53.695 --> 00:19:56.274
a OROBORTA,

00:19:56.837 --> 00:20:02.248
di KRITSHTOMOTINA, toyf-muter.

00:20:02.659 --> 00:20:05.524
iz zi iz zeyer a fayne froy,

00:20:05.524 --> 00:20:08.593
un zi vet dir tsunemen bay zikh nekhtikn.

00:20:09.831 --> 00:20:10.854
gut.

00:20:10.894 --> 00:20:12.491
bin ikh avek bay ir,

00:20:13.341 --> 00:20:15.360
un zi hot mir take tsugenumen,

00:20:15.484 --> 00:20:19.443
ober esn hot zi aleyn nit gehat, s'dokh alts geven oyf kartlekh.

00:20:20.091 --> 00:20:21.620
ober eyn tog

00:20:21.660 --> 00:20:22.818
zogt zi,

00:20:22.825 --> 00:20:24.000
ikh gey

00:20:24.951 --> 00:20:27.324
ikh gey in

00:20:27.685 --> 00:20:31.779
in kloyster UNK da- davenen, vi ken men dos zogn?

00:20:32.713 --> 00:20:35.002
iz zi avek un mir farshlosn,

00:20:35.160 --> 00:20:38.178
un ikh bin gelegn hungerikerheyt oyfn

00:20:38.178 --> 00:20:39.334
oyfn sofe,

00:20:39.334 --> 00:20:44.571
ikh vart ikh vart, in der fri iz zi avek un zi iz nito un nito, s'shoyn fir a zeyger un zi iz nito.

00:20:45.032 --> 00:20:48.806
ikh her nor az s'geyen shvere trit, menerishe trit.

00:20:49.133 --> 00:20:50.578
shtivl trit.

00:20:51.158 --> 00:20:55.067
un s'hot zikh geefnt, zey hobn geefnt di tir un s'arayn efsher fir mener.

00:20:55.140 --> 00:20:57.828
v- militerishe ongeton

00:20:57.828 --> 00:21:00.467
un zey hobn gezogt, ir zayt aza un aza.

00:21:00.557 --> 00:21:01.546
litvish?

00:21:01.398 --> 00:21:02.576
litvishe.

00:21:02.802 --> 00:21:08.854
zog ikh, yo, far vos zayt ir nit in geto? ayer ort iz in geto! ah kumt mit undz!

00:21:09.400 --> 00:21:11.301
un zey hobn mir arestirt,

00:21:11.661 --> 00:21:13.579
un zey hobn mir avekgefirt

00:21:13.585 --> 00:21:16.127
vu i- vu es iz der

00:21:17.297 --> 00:21:18.978
vu es iz der

00:21:20.689 --> 00:21:22.286
shtot-farvaltung.

00:21:22.765 --> 00:21:24.480
un dortn iz geven

00:21:24.604 --> 00:21:25.998
Geshtapo

00:21:28.502 --> 00:21:30.723
oder Zikherhayts-Politsey.

00:21:34.240 --> 00:21:36.849
un nu vos iz dortn pasirt mit aykh?

00:21:36.653 --> 00:21:40.022
un un un dortn hobn zey mir genumen fregn,

00:21:42.137 --> 00:21:50.082
vu, ver hot mir, hobn zey glaykh genumen un farzukht un tsugenumen dem dokument. ver hot mir gegebn dem dem litvishn dokument?

00:21:50.082 --> 00:21:50.855
ver?

00:21:51.148 --> 00:21:52.711
ver hot dos mir geholfn?

00:21:52.954 --> 00:21:54.247
hob ikh gezogt,

00:21:54.338 --> 00:21:55.513
hob ikh gezogt,

00:21:55.772 --> 00:21:57.251
Fromas.

00:21:57.510 --> 00:21:59.996
hot er mir derlangt a khap farn ⟨khakhod⟩,

00:21:59.996 --> 00:22:04.088
un derlangt a vorf fun eyn breg bizn tsveytn, un ikh bin geven a ⟨magerinke⟩

00:22:04.088 --> 00:22:07.140
az ikh hob gemeynt ikh vel durkh durkhn durkhn fentster oyf in droysn.

00:22:07.753 --> 00:22:09.181
zogt er, du

00:22:09.255 --> 00:22:11.746
du meynst az mir zaynen naronim?

00:22:11.888 --> 00:22:15.285
un un vos makhstu fun undz

00:22:15.285 --> 00:22:18.648
azelkhene nu!

00:22:19.330 --> 00:22:20.691
shpasn, yo?

00:22:19.448 --> 00:22:22.581
shpasn, az du meynst az mir zaynen naronim?

00:22:22.688 --> 00:22:26.951
un er hot mir derlangt a yog hin un tsurik, ikh hob gemeynt az s'vet fun mir nit blaybn.

00:22:27.092 --> 00:22:30.261
un arunter geshlept in keler. dortn zaynen gezesn

00:22:30.261 --> 00:22:34.683
alerleyike ⟨spopularitn⟩ un banditn un

00:22:34.683 --> 00:22:36.115
un ganovim,

00:22:36.137 --> 00:22:39.118
ober lang bin ikh dortn nit gezesn, a tsvey dray teg.

00:22:39.259 --> 00:22:43.961
un nakher hot men mir aroysgerufn un m'hot mir avekgefirt

00:22:44.524 --> 00:22:45.615
in turme.

00:22:45.773 --> 00:22:47.727
geyendik fun turme,

00:22:47.727 --> 00:22:50.222
geyendik tsum turme, unter vegs,

00:22:52.152 --> 00:22:53.664
zog ikh tsu im,

00:22:54.109 --> 00:22:55.971
dos iz geven aza sheyner

00:22:55.971 --> 00:22:58.170
tog, aza heyser tog,

00:22:58.783 --> 00:23:08.272
zog ikh im tsu im, her aykh ayn, loz mir avek, keyner zet dokh nit, nor ikh un du. makht er a zets, dort hob ikh a tsetl un ikh muz brengen a untershrift az ikh hob dikh gebrakht in turme, mit a shtempl.

00:23:08.272 --> 00:23:09.825
ikh vil oykh, zogt er, lebn.

00:23:09.825 --> 00:23:11.765
ikh hob im gezogt, ikh vil azoy lebn.

00:23:11.765 --> 00:23:13.290
zogt er, ikh vil oykh lebn.

00:23:13.920 --> 00:23:15.905
nu un er hot mir gebrakht in turme,

00:23:16.924 --> 00:23:18.555
un dortn in turme,

00:23:18.882 --> 00:23:19.748
hinter,

00:23:19.748 --> 00:23:22.456
in nit eyn toyer, meynt nit az dos iz eyn toyer,

00:23:22.456 --> 00:23:24.118
baym ersht iz eyn toyer,

00:23:24.118 --> 00:23:29.771
nakher a hoyf, nakher nokh a toyer, efsher dray toyern darf men durkhgeyn m'zol zitsn in tfise.

00:23:29.771 --> 00:23:32.994
un geyendik hob ikh getrakht, s'rikhtik der shprikhvort,

00:23:32.994 --> 00:23:33.880
az fun

00:23:33.880 --> 00:23:37.742
turme fun a UNK iz der mentsh nit zikher af zayn lebn.

00:23:38.170 --> 00:23:41.539
ot azoy hob ikh getrakht di harts, azelkhe gedanken iz mir geblibn.

00:23:42.928 --> 00:23:46.719
un un dortn iz gezesn nokh eyner.

00:23:46.962 --> 00:23:49.051
Nina Blekher.

00:23:49.051 --> 00:23:50.972
dem dokter Blekher's a tokhter.

00:23:51.113 --> 00:23:53.874
ir hot men arestirt

00:23:53.982 --> 00:23:58.498
far dem vos zi, in ir hot zikh gelibt a daytsh.

00:23:58.960 --> 00:24:01.147
a a ofitsir.

00:24:01.980 --> 00:24:04.117
sheyn iz zi geven vi halb di velt.

00:24:04.258 --> 00:24:10.381
ober fun, di geto hot gehat zeyer fil nuts fun im. er flegt alts dertseyln vos velkhe

00:24:10.381 --> 00:24:13.064
zakhn, velkhe

00:24:13.064 --> 00:24:15.949
frages es veln, vos es vet zayn forkumen.

00:24:15.949 --> 00:24:18.261
un er flegt farn geto shafn zayne

00:24:18.261 --> 00:24:19.738
shpayz,

00:24:19.738 --> 00:24:26.994
ober a tsveyter hot zikh in ir farlibt, un tsishn zey iz geven a kamf, un un m'hot ir mit eyner vort aroysgegebn

00:24:26.994 --> 00:24:31.432
un m'hot ir, bay nakht flegt kumen aza shvartse mashin,

00:24:31.432 --> 00:24:32.824
der shvartser

00:24:32.824 --> 00:24:35.336
vorem, hot zikh dos ongerufn, a shvartser

00:24:35.781 --> 00:24:38.340
vorem, m'hot ir aroysgefirt, opgeshosn.

00:24:38.818 --> 00:24:40.359
un mir hobn

00:24:40.359 --> 00:24:43.689
un ikh bin gezen, un nokh eyne hob ikh gefunen, Zelde Malinke.

00:24:43.780 --> 00:24:47.419
velkhe iz itster in Izrael, nor di familye nomen di

00:24:47.475 --> 00:24:51.570
als froy, als farheyrater veys ikh nit.

00:24:52.673 --> 00:24:53.966
iz

00:24:54.597 --> 00:24:55.876
zaynen mir gezesn.

00:24:55.876 --> 00:24:57.662
oykh farmishpet tsum toyt.

00:24:58.225 --> 00:24:59.265
az m'vet

00:25:00.891 --> 00:25:02.437
az m'hot ongehoybn,

00:25:03.068 --> 00:25:06.690
eyn mol mitvokh iz geven di ershte nakht hot men bombardirt Shavl,

00:25:07.472 --> 00:25:08.731
hot zikh

00:25:09.261 --> 00:25:13.760
hot zikh a SAMALYOT velkhe hot arumgedreyt zikh ibern turme,

00:25:13.227 --> 00:25:14.807
an eroplan, yo?

00:25:14.357 --> 00:25:15.872
a eroplan,

00:25:15.872 --> 00:25:19.669
un er hot gezen az dos iz a f- turme, hot er nit bombardirt.

00:25:19.669 --> 00:25:20.892
ober in geto

00:25:20.892 --> 00:25:21.627
hot er

00:25:21.627 --> 00:25:24.613
tsvishn andere zogndik ⟨aregevorfn⟩ a bombe.

00:25:24.613 --> 00:25:25.910
un getrofn

00:25:25.984 --> 00:25:33.183
eynem a mitglid fun yidishn farvaltung, fun yidishe gemeynde,

00:25:33.358 --> 00:25:36.423
Leybovitsh, Mendl Leybovitsh.

00:25:36.632 --> 00:25:37.827
velkher iz

00:25:37.827 --> 00:25:39.191
geshtorbn nakher.

00:25:42.370 --> 00:25:45.013
velkher iz geshtorbn fun fun di vundn.

00:25:47.365 --> 00:25:49.080
a- af morgn,

00:25:50.588 --> 00:25:52.500
az m'hot undz aroysgelozn

00:25:52.500 --> 00:25:55.476
afn hoyf arumts- arumgeyn,

00:25:56.460 --> 00:25:58.850
kumt tsu geyn der galekh Bozhele,

00:25:59.768 --> 00:26:00.684
un er zogt

00:26:00.684 --> 00:26:03.491
tsu undz beydn, tsu mir un tsu Zelde Malinke,

00:26:04.324 --> 00:26:09.111
nu, di ershte nakht zaynen a sakh mentshn antlofn.

00:26:09.758 --> 00:26:12.572
ober far vos zayt ir nit antlofn? zogn mir,

00:26:12.572 --> 00:26:14.510
undzer kamer iz geven farmakht.

00:26:15.293 --> 00:26:17.632
zogt er, ikh vel aykh helfn.

00:26:17.723 --> 00:26:19.641
di kameres zoln zayn ofn.

00:26:20.794 --> 00:26:22.340
un

00:26:22.633 --> 00:26:25.867
mir dakht zikh, mir dakht zikh dos iz geven a shabesdiker tog.

00:26:26.093 --> 00:26:29.681
un for dem hot er gebrakht shtrik, zeyer grobe,

00:26:30.362 --> 00:26:33.376
un er hot undz gezogt vi m'darf makhn dem leyter,

00:26:33.653 --> 00:26:38.991
zog ikh, er vet dokh arumflien der leyter, shtrik zenen dokh laykht, vi azoy veln mir

00:26:38.991 --> 00:26:41.311
arumflien hin un tsurik? zogt er,

00:26:41.311 --> 00:26:45.324
un do halt mikh azoy, un dortn iz do di di

00:26:45.853 --> 00:26:51.992
hiltserne nu shislen vi men git zey esn,

00:26:51.992 --> 00:26:56.444
oyf velkhe hobn optsamungen in UNK geyt es, azelkhe lange,

00:26:56.586 --> 00:27:01.392
zogt er, dortn vet ir dos a- araynhakn in der erd, in dem dem hiltsernem shisl,

00:27:01.392 --> 00:27:04.041
un ir vet onbindn dem leyter,

00:27:04.041 --> 00:27:06.817
un dan ariber varfn oyf yener zayt,

00:27:06.817 --> 00:27:11.593
un ot azoy vet eyner dortn velkher iz shoyn aropgeshprungen onhaltn,

00:27:11.593 --> 00:27:13.404
un azoy veln ale aribergeyn.

00:27:13.663 --> 00:27:16.546
nu, nisht a- s'geven a rey.

00:27:16.546 --> 00:27:18.140
m'hot gedarft shteyn in a rey.

00:27:18.140 --> 00:27:20.306
a sakh hobn gevolt antloyfn.

00:27:20.616 --> 00:27:21.960
iz

00:27:22.557 --> 00:27:25.886
shteyendik in rey bin ikh arayn un aroys,

00:27:25.886 --> 00:27:30.481
ikh hob gehat moyre tsu shpringen, s'iz fun hoykh, fun zeyer hoykh geven tsu shpringen.

00:27:30.775 --> 00:27:35.122
shteyt hinter mir a litvisher mentsh, a elterer shoyn

00:27:35.162 --> 00:27:37.687
zogt er, oyber ir vilt nit,

00:27:38.149 --> 00:27:40.286
PANALE, dos heyst

00:27:40.174 --> 00:27:41.096
froy.

00:27:40.326 --> 00:27:42.176
fro- froylayn,

00:27:41.659 --> 00:27:42.817
froylayn.

00:27:42.216 --> 00:27:43.816
oyber ir vilt nit,

00:27:43.816 --> 00:27:46.024
git mir avek ayere rey.

00:27:46.519 --> 00:27:49.790
zog, trakht ikh, s'mikh a shande,

00:27:49.790 --> 00:27:58.540
a elterer mentsh hot nit moyre un ikh hob moyre. zogt er, ikh vel aykh zogn vi m'darf shpringen, m'darf aynbreng- aynbeygn di fis iber di kni,

00:27:58.540 --> 00:28:04.569
un dem gantsn gut in for- in foroys derlangen azoy vi m'shpringt aroys fun a fun a ban.

00:28:04.963 --> 00:28:07.134
vi a vi a frosh.

00:28:07.562 --> 00:28:09.901
un ot azoy zogt er vet es zayn zeyer laykht.

00:28:09.908 --> 00:28:12.883
un ikh hob gehat moyre vayle di nakht, di ershte nakht,

00:28:12.883 --> 00:28:14.722
iz geven a yidishe froy

00:28:15.730 --> 00:28:18.339
Vinik, kovner zaynen zey geven,

00:28:18.362 --> 00:28:24.853
froy Vinik mit ir tokhter, zey hot men gekhapt unter vegs tsvishn eyn dorf un tsveytn dorf hot men zey gekhapt.

00:28:24.910 --> 00:28:27.623
iz zi mit di tokhter ge- geshprungen,

00:28:27.623 --> 00:28:29.513
zeyer kamer iz geven ofn,

00:28:29.513 --> 00:28:34.016
un di f- muter iz derharget gevorn, di tokhter iz antlofn.

00:28:34.495 --> 00:28:36.145
iz hob ikh gehat moyre.

00:28:36.145 --> 00:28:39.081
ober az er hot mir shoyn azoy gezogt, hob ikh rizikirt.

00:28:39.081 --> 00:28:41.492
ikh bin aropgeshprungen azoy laykht,

00:28:41.768 --> 00:28:43.821
vi a vi af a kisn.

00:28:44.721 --> 00:28:48.124
az s'bashert, dos iz alts un ikh gloyb in bashertkeyt.

00:28:48.332 --> 00:28:49.541
un nakher

00:28:49.699 --> 00:28:55.143
hot men nor gedarft, nokh arum un arum iz dortn do a a a arum arum a tsam,

00:28:55.504 --> 00:29:00.057
mit shtekhl-drot oyf oybn, hot men nokh gedarft iber dem tsam ariber krikhn.

00:29:00.057 --> 00:29:03.474
hob ikh zikh tserisn di fis ot o do, hoykh oyf a di kni.

00:29:03.474 --> 00:29:05.356
hob ikh arunter gerisn fun di

00:29:05.356 --> 00:29:06.680
di untershte,

00:29:06.680 --> 00:29:08.039
kleyd di untershtn.

00:29:08.613 --> 00:29:10.432
un ikh hob farbundn,

00:29:10.894 --> 00:29:13.067
un gegangen vayter

